              "Please revise your prompt and record it in the space below.": "my resolution and topic to be discussed is: \"Should a high school ban all smartphones during school hours?\"\n\ndeep dive into this topic and talk to me abt it from multiple facets. analyze relevant definitions in the resolutions, such as what constitutes smartphones, school time, etc. analyze both the affirmative and negative perspective on this topic. give me direct reasons that tie directly to the topic, and also tie those subpoints into bigger impacts with quantifiable magnitude and scope. back these up with empirics, analytics, and more. give me key clash points and likely hotspots of disagreement. if i were discussing this with others, give me a directions in which the conversation would go and what would be most conducive to discussion. tell me a bit about the importance of discussion about the topic and about opinions and perspectives in general.",
